Situated at 58 Von Braun Street, Steiltes, the spa boasts two luxurious treatment rooms ideal for couples who are ready to relax and be completely pampered. Shandon Spa has a team of professional therapists with years of experience and passion for treating their clients with a variety of treatments on offer.  Restore your well-being by indulging in an array of treatments: from body massages, exfoliations, body wraps and scrubs, to facials, Bellabaci cupping massages and facials, and much more.  These treatments are sure to relax, restore and rejuvenate both the body and mind. Shandon Spa has partnered with product ranges such as Esse Skincare, The Spa Warehouse, Bellabaci and Faby Nails, which are anti-cruelty, vegan-friendly and organic.  Shandon Spa is a true haven for your well-being.    